{"tid":992153,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本某男子購買街頭女歌手CD後當面踩爛，男子稱不能在街頭販買","createTime":"2019-01-23T03:02:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-23T14:48:18.000Z","uid":100680,"like":5,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"f5e95203ff042521521a2999cabe659c3a20663d","tid":992153,"uid":100680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T03:02:29.000Z","msg":"文／厭世小羊<br />\n<br />\n小羊去日本的時候，常常會在街上看到很多業餘的街頭歌手，在人行道或車站外現場表演，與一般街頭藝人不同的是，他們不會要求路人丟錢，而是販售他們的個人CD來為生。<br />\n<br />\n日本網友「Gretchen」就在推特上發佈了一段影片，內文打著「我朋友不小心踩到花1000日圓買的CD」，影片只見一位女街頭歌手，在秋葉原的街道上，宣傳她的CD，Gretchen的朋友用1000日圓買下了CD，本來女街頭歌手以為對方是欣賞自己的作品才買的，沒想到下一秒，這名男子就將CD丟到地上，狠狠的踩踏。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s1.imgs.cc/img/aaaaa1wI4.jpg?_w=750\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs1.imgs.cc%2Fimg%2Faaaaa1wI4.jpg%3F_w%3D750&h=62d5dd4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://s1.imgs.cc/img/aaaaa1wI6.jpg?_w=750\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs1.imgs.cc%2Fimg%2Faaaaa1wI6.jpg%3F_w%3D750&h=ca536cdd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s1.imgs.cc/img/aaaaa1wI5.jpg?_w=750\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs1.imgs.cc%2Fimg%2Faaaaa1wI5.jpg%3F_w%3D750&h=db2e06a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://s1.imgs.cc/img/aaaaa1wI0.jpg?_w=750\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs1.imgs.cc%2Fimg%2Faaaaa1wI0.jpg%3F_w%3D750&h=e8a9b82f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n事後有網友發現他的推特用戶名原本是「驅逐違法街頭演唱」，所以根本就是故意要來踩踏CD的，影片傳開後，他與朋友也遭到網友痛罵而被肉搜，畢竟有沒有違法是一件事，但公然汙辱對方又是另一回事了！<br />\n<br />\n意外的是，有不少日本網友看了覺得「花錢買的東西要怎麼處理那是個人自由」，也有人覺得這樣羞辱他人很差勁，怎麼可以這樣對待一個女孩子？<br />\n<br />\n小羊個人是覺得，的確買的東西要怎麼處理，都是自己的自由，不過花大錢我就是大爺的想法，我倒是不太能認同，畢竟人家為了生活也是很努力啊！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原文網址: 花錢就是大爺？日男和街頭女歌手買CD　當場丟地上當垃圾用力猛踩 | 厭世小羊 | 鍵盤大檸檬 | ETtoday新聞雲 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/dalemon/post/41230#ixzz5dObaREdQ \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fdalemon%2Fpost%2F41230%23ixzz5dObaREdQ%20&d=PD6BU5FT0PaiJLYkH2SYQiwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=8955144b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/dalemon/post/41230#ixzz5dObaREdQ </a>"},{"pid":"061faf3a60a33e16c9681ac063b458f621ff1c95","tid":992153,"uid":92376,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T03:04:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/fd76sNnnePM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Ffd76sNnnePM&d=PD6BU5FT0PaiJLYkH2SYQiwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=419dc362\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/fd76sNnnePM</a><br />\n整爛cd既經典案例"},{"pid":"1b137d768e0d6ff6a2bd9b164655026d4793b47b","tid":992153,"uid":100680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T03:05:31.000Z","msg":"那位街頭女歌手推特<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/ibura2525/status/1076346375342702592\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fibura2525%2Fstatus%2F1076346375342702592&d=PD6BU5FT0PaiJLYkH2SYQiwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=6e52f081\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fibura2525%2Fstatus%2F1076346375342702592&h=3f060879\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/ibura2525/status/1076346375342702592</a>"},{"pid":"17bab6e763265b8b93b6a1ad5c085fa9478a052c","tid":992153,"uid":21423,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T03:05:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fd9edbe7178467eaed915528874b0446f23f075c","tid":992153,"uid":50882,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T03:17:47.000Z","msg":"如果見到香港班乞衣應該一腳踢爛個乞衣兜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10c8301cef04153a8a4e24c3dc074fa91a8aa650","tid":992153,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T03:19:35.000Z","msg":"諗起爆粗band友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56353967263e323dd83445a15129d53ba8bbdb78","tid":992153,"uid":65530,"like":0,"dislike":0,